Place breed images here as {slug}.jpg
e.g., labrador-retriever.jpg, french-bulldog.jpg, persian-cat.jpg

Either:
  - Run scripts/fetch-breed-images.js with a free Pexels API key, or
  - Drop your own licensed JPGs (1200x800 recommended)

The site automatically renders any image that exists at /assets/images/breeds/{slug}.jpg
provided the slug has an entry in /assets/data/breed-images.js.
